    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "System Timetable\nEffective April 1-May 1, 2001\nBEST PLACE TO WORK.\nBEST AIRLINE TO FLY.\nWHAT A COINCIDENCE.\nRanked among Fortune 100's Best Places to Work\nfor the 3rd year in a row, and again named\nAir Transport World's \"Airline of the Year.\"\nFORTUNE®\n100 BEST\nGO MOAN FORE\n2001\ni Transport world\nAirline of the Year\nContinental Airlines\nWork Hard.\nFly Right..",
      "For reservations call your\ntravel agent or\n1-800-523-FARE\n(1-800-523-3273)\nFor complete vacation packages\ncall Continental Airlines Vacations at\n1-800-634-5555\nFor automated flight\ninformation call\n1-800-784-4444\nAlways ask for an\n#TICKET.\nPurchase tickets online or\ndownload the timetable at\nwww.continental.com\nContinental\nAirlines\nATT040101"
    ],
